    "title": "Industrial Epoxy Floors - Elite South Texas",
    "content": "Industrial\nOur engineered flooring solutions are designed for industrial, manufacturing and warehouse facilities. These protective coatings offer extreme durability to withstand heavy traffic and industrial machinery. Seamless flooring systems are fluid-applied in place. Vertical applications are available, including cove base for containment purposes.\nAdvantages\nQuick install options available for minimal downtime\nEasy to maintain\nVariable coefficient of friction (COF) ranges to meet or exceed ADA Flat Surfaces, ADA Inclined Surfaces recommendations\nSuitable for high traffic and heavy machinery\nFDA, USDA* and CFIA** acceptable\nFor new or existing construction\nAntimicrobial and antibacterial\nSuitable for extreme hot and cold environments\nStain resistant to acids, oils, petrochemicals, cleaning chemicals, etc.\nMultiple finishes and colors available\n* Can be used in USDA facilities based on FSIS Directive 11,000.4 (Rev. 1), November 24, 1995.\n** Agriculture Canada (also known as Canadian Food Inspection Agency).\nWarehouses\nManufacturing plants\nAssembly lines\nAutomotive service areas\nAerospace facilities\nFood processing plants\nElectronic manufacturing\nParamount",
